I archived files (posted and external) from 8ch Brenton Tarrant Memetic Warfare 1-17 + HTML. Will upload somewhere in a few days.

Any simple way to archive ZeroNet threads and files?
8ch on ZeroNet is much more relaxed, must be the effect of overnight eugenics coupled with delousing. Similar to the early Internet.
